node.text:
Little Flower: FINAL Part (4/4) 

Come, come little flower,
wind of winter has come with shiver, 
come inside by the hearth of fire, 
little flower I hope you'll remember, 
hearth of fire your home forever

Little steps my brave soldier, 
take a breather, my heart's desire, 
little orange bloom ,I'll take us through, 
from day and night and winter breeze, 

Little flower sweet flower, 
the earth is ripe for your grandeur, 
think me not in melancholy, 
in every moment we spent in glee, 
little flower I'm here, always remember, 
this hearth you once called home forever... 

Poem by @nate.wordsmyth

🏆PRIZE🎁
1st winner: a KAMVAS16 (2021) pendisplay 
2nd winner: a pet portrait commission 
3rd winner (x3): Personalize Mao Avatar 

To you all that has been reading & enjoying my comics, Mao says a great big Thank You! My journey has become much more meaningful and memorable with you guys tagging along with Mao.

In celebration of hitting 300K, I'll be teaming with @huiontablet to hold a giveaway with the Grand prize of a brand new Kamvas 16 (2021) pen display. I've used the Kamvas to create a mini comic (this post) and found it quite enjoyable! You can check out my full review of the Huion Kamvas 16 (2021) and watch the unboxing video from my previous post too. 💕

📌📌GIVEAWAY RULES
1. Follow @bichi.mao and @huiontablet
2. Like and share this post on your story 
3. Tag your friends in the comment section (The more tags the more entries, ghost account will be disqualified)

Winner will be announced in 7 days. Huion will provide free shipping for the pendisplay (Though the winner may have to pay any tariffs). 

Good luck everyone! 🥰
